275
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:17,530
Yuzu.

276
00:15:18,530 --> 00:15:21,730
Don't worry. She's not mad, or anything.

277
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:25,410
But Kimari-san cried.

278
00:15:25,410 --> 00:15:27,230
I think she felt hurt.

279
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,540
It's all on you.

280
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:31,610
